_source.body: Philosopher Eric Hoffer said, ‚ÄúWhen freedom destroys order, the yearning for order will destroy freedom.‚Äù What he was alluding to was that whether left or right will make no difference. There is no difference between authoritarian government from the right or the left: the results are the same. An elite, an authoritarianism as such, will gradually but forcefully entrap society so that it will not go into chaos. And most people will accept it because they desire personal peace and safety.
